{
  "stem": "1733.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --my brother-in-law and myself got lodging for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got a little house-- little house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we told the people that we are going to go home to Russia-- I mean, to the Carpathians, to take home-- to bring back my brother-in-law's three sisters and my two sisters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I left Joe in Zatec, and I went back to Loucky to get them together to bring them back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, the borders were starting to close already, and there was no transportation from Munkacs to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had to go by wagon over the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were smuggled over the border into Koseca.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And at Koseca, we got a train and went to Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Were happy times for the girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My sister-in-law Helen, and Elaine, and my two sisters, Magda and Esther, they had a lot of fun on the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was-- and I warned them, I says, please, don't make yourself known on the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Don't make any-- Don't make any moves that people should notice you, because the Russian soldiers were on those trains, and there were raping the young girls.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And these kids didn't want to listen to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I took my belt, and I beat up my sister-in-law-- presently she was a young girl-- and my sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they were behaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it was a big responsibility at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we got-- we got to Zatec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were there, and we were living and waiting for the papers from the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was working in Zatec in a government office that was-- I was in charge of about six or eight people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a-- it was called [NON-ENGLISH], which is a-- it's not a town.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
